mm.icl.hlc.HLCReasoner

Class HLCReasoner

  • java.lang.Object
    • mm.icl.hlc.HLCReasoner.AbstractReasoner
      • mm.icl.hlc.HLCReasoner.HLCReasoner

  • public class HLCReasoner
extends AbstractReasoner
    HLC Reasoner: Component of HLCA which performs a consistency check on the unclassified PhysicalActivity and Nutrition Context instance and classifies it in order to identify the context type to which the instance belongs.
    Since:
    2015-10-28
    Version:
    2.5
    Author:
    Claudia Villalonga and Muhammad Asif Razzaq
